    <body>
      <section eId="sec_980_A">
        <num>980-A</num>
        <heading>Contents of the district plan</heading>
        <subsection eId="sec_980_A__subsec_a">
          <num>(a)</num>
          <content>
            <p>a map of the district;\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_980_A__subsec_b">
          <num>(b)</num>
          <content>
            <p>the written report or reports of the legislative body containing:\n</p>
          </content>
          <paragraph eId="sec_980_A__subsec_b__subsec_1">
            <num>(1)</num>
            <content>
              <p>a description of the boundaries of the district proposed for\nestablishment or extension in a manner sufficient to identify the lands\nincluded;\n</p>
            </content>
          </paragraph>
          <paragraph eId="sec_980_A__subsec_b__subsec_2">
            <num>(2)</num>
            <content>
              <p>a description of the present and proposed uses of these lands;\n</p>
            </content>
          </paragraph>
          <paragraph eId="sec_980_A__subsec_b__subsec_3">
            <num>(3)</num>
            <content>
              <p>the improvements proposed and the maximum cost thereof;\n</p>
            </content>
          </paragraph>
          <paragraph eId="sec_980_A__subsec_b__subsec_4">
            <num>(4)</num>
            <content>
              <p>the total annual amount proposed to be expended for improvements,\nmaintenance and operation;\n</p>
            </content>
          </paragraph>
          <paragraph eId="sec_980_A__subsec_b__subsec_5">
            <num>(5)</num>
            <content>
              <p>the proposed source or sources of financing;\n</p>
            </content>
          </paragraph>
          <paragraph eId="sec_980_A__subsec_b__subsec_6">
            <num>(6)</num>
            <content>
              <p>the proposed time for implementation and completion of the\ndistrict plan;\n</p>
            </content>
          </paragraph>
          <paragraph eId="sec_980_A__subsec_b__subsec_7">
            <num>(7)</num>
            <content>
              <p>any proposed rules and regulations to be applicable to the\ndistrict;\n</p>
            </content>
          </paragraph>
          <paragraph eId="sec_980_A__subsec_b__subsec_8">
            <num>(8)</num>
            <content>
              <p>a list of the properties to be benefited, and a statement of the\nmethod or methods by which the expenses of a district will be imposed\nupon benefited real property, in proportion to the benefit received by\nsuch property, to defray the cost thereof, including operation and\nmaintenance. Notwithstanding any inconsistent provision of section nine\nhundred eighty-f of this article, the plan may provide that all or any\nclass or category of real property which is exempt by law from real\nproperty taxation and which would not benefit from the establishment or\nextension of the district may nevertheless be included within the\nboundaries of the district but such property shall not be subject to any\ndistrict charge;\n</p>
            </content>
          </paragraph>
          <paragraph eId="sec_980_A__subsec_b__subsec_9">
            <num>(9)</num>
            <content>
              <p>a statement identifying the district management association for\nthe district; and\n</p>
            </content>
          </paragraph>
          <paragraph eId="sec_980_A__subsec_b__subsec_10">
            <num>(10)</num>
            <content>
              <p>any other item or matter required to be incorporated therein by\nthe legislative body.\n</p>
            </content>
          </paragraph>
        </subsection>
      </section>
